OL,3,CMan jailed for six years after raping
OL,4,Cand sexually assaulting a woman
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced for six years
OL,7,Fafter raping and sexually assaulting a
OL,8,Fwoman in Bath.
OL,10,FPaul Kibble was convicted of two
OL,11,Fsexual offences at a property in
OL,12,FOctober 2023.
OL,14,FThe court heard during the trial that
OL,15,Fthe 42-year-old 'refused to take no
OL,16,Ffor an answer' and continued to engage
OL,17,Fin sexual activity for his own
OL,18,Fgratification without the woman's
OL,19,Fconsent.
