OL,6,FThe victim shared a statement with the
OL,7,Fcourt ahead of Mr Kibble's sentencing
OL,8,Fto explain the impact of his actions.
OL,10,FShe said: "It has affected me in so
OL,11,Fmany different ways, words cannot even
OL,12,Fdescribe how I feel each day.
OL,14,F"I cannot step into town to go
OL,15,Fshopping; I am scared in my own home,
OL,16,Fand I have been unable to return to
OL,17,Fwork since the assault.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
