OL,6,F"I feel like something has been taken
OL,7,Ffrom me, something that I am never
OL,8,Fgoing to be able to get back, but I
OL,9,Fhope that this result will encourage
OL,10,Fothers to speak up."
OL,12,FOn Friday 31 May, the jury returned
OL,13,Fguilty verdicts by a majority at
OL,14,FBristol Crown Court for rape and
OL,15,Fsexual assault by penetration.
OL,17,FKibble, who lived in Bath, will also
OL,18,Fbe placed on the sex offenders'
OL,19,Fregister indefinitely.
