OL,6,FDetective Constable Alice Chandler of
OL,7,FOperation Bluestone, Avon and Somerset
OL,8,FPolice's dedicated rape and serious
OL,9,Fsexual offences investigative team,
OL,10,Fsaid: "The bravery and strength the
OL,11,Fvictim has shown throughout this case
OL,12,Fhas been truly commendable.
OL,14,F"She has shown a tremendous level of
OL,15,Fcourage from the day of reporting
OL,16,Fright until the verdicts were
OL,17,Freceived, demonstrating dignity and
OL,18,Frespect throughout the investigation
OL,19,Fand trial despite being the victim of
OL,20,Fsuch horrific offences.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
