OL,4,Cand sexually assaulting a woman
OL,6,F"We never underestimate the bravery it
OL,7,Ftakes for victims of sexual offences
OL,8,Fto come forward to police and to give
OL,9,Fevidence in court at trial.
OL,11,F"Kibble has continually denied
OL,12,Fresponsibility for his actions, and it
OL,13,Fis thanks to the victim's continued
OL,14,Fsupport and fortitude that we have
OL,15,Fbeen able to ensure a dangerous man is
OL,16,Fno longer on our streets."
