OL,6,FDC Chandler added the work of support
OL,7,Fagencies has been invaluable and hopes
OL,8,Fthis verdict and sentence gives
OL,9,Fconfidence to all victims of sexual
OL,10,Foffences to report crimes to us.
OL,12,FShe said: "Throughout this
OL,13,Finvestigation, we have worked in
OL,14,Fcollaboration with numerous agencies
OL,15,Fwhose services have been invaluable
OL,16,Fand the positive result in this case
OL,17,Fgoes far in reinforcing the need for
OL,18,Feffective multi-agency working.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
