OL,4,Cand sexually assaulting a woman
OL,6,F"Independent advisors have been able
OL,7,Fto support her throughout the
OL,8,Finvestigation, which often is a great
OL,9,Fsource of help for victims who are
OL,10,Fgoing through this process.
OL,12,F"Hopefully cases like this give
OL,13,Fconfidence to any victim of a sexual
OL,14,Foffence to come forward.
OL,16,F"It does not matter if you report
OL,17,Fsomething to us five minutes after it
OL,18,Fhappens or five years.
OL,20,F"You will be believed and those crimes
OL,21,Fwill be thoroughly investigated."
